platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Lots of apps can offer driving directionsbut what if youre not driving at all? Thats where Transit comes in. The travel planning app shows you how to get from point A to point B via train, bus, rideshareand now even bikeshare and scooter. The app will seek out your best route, offer a few alternate options, and let you know how long you can expect to be in transit.

This travel planning app shows you how to get from A to B via train, bus, ride-share  even bike-share and scooter. It will find you the best route, offer a few alternates, and let you know how long itll take.

Whether youre commuting to work, or hopping a metro in a new city, Transit is your indispensable guide to public transit systems, car- and bike-share services, and more. In addition to live trip-planning updates, Transit will tell you when to leave and give exact step-by-step directions to get you where you need to go.

Cette app de planification de voyages vous montre comment vous rendre dun point A  un point B en train, bus ou covoiturage, et mme en empruntant un vlo ou en scooter. Lapp vous propose le meilleur itinraire, ainsi que des alternatives et vous indique le temps de trajet.
